Feature: Submit a new application
  As a user
  I want to submit a new application
  So that I can complete the form submission process

  Scenario: Successfully submit a new application
    Given I go to the URL
    And I login using the credentials provided
    When I click "Submit a new application" button
    And I continue with the submission if prompted
    And I fill out the forms
    And I click "Next screen" button
    Then I verify all the inputted values are displayed in the Summary screen
    When I click "Validate and send" button
    Then I verify I am redirected to "Thank you for submitting your project" page
